directions: On the 3rd floor of Collier-Scripps Hall, from the main stairs, walk all the way down the main corridor. Room 301 is the last door on the right.
On the 2nd floor of Collier-Scripps Hall, from the main stairs, walk all the way down the main corridor. Room 207 is the last door on the right.
On the 2nd floor of Collier-Scripps Hall, from the main stairs, Room 235 is the first door on the right.
You can find refreshments, vendor tables, and student posters throughout the corridors on the 3rd floor of Collier-Scripps Hall.
Enter the Shivers Basketball Practice Facility Hospitality Suite using the entryway just east of the Knapp Center arena and just west of the Mediacom Stadium
